title: The Milk Carton Kids, Live From The Newport Folk Festival, 2013
description: Half Simon & Garfunkel and half Smothers Brothers, Joey Ryan and Kenneth Pattengale's melancholic harmonies intertwine beautifully, while their playful, deadpan banter is worth the price of admission on its own. "Hope Of A Lifetime"  "The Ash & Clay"  "Honey, Honey"  "Charlie" "Michigan"  "Girls, Gather 'Round'  "New York"  "Snake Eyes"  "I Still Want A Little More"  "Memphis"
